# 2. Use the descriptive patch below as a guide for manual edits
#
# Each hunk is labeled with the file, roughly which function/section it
# touches, and what the edit does. The full v2 implementations in
# scripts-v2/ are the authoritative source for the exact replacement text.
# ----------------------------------------------------------------------


